<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_163d7175-0092-43b7-864c-dd4eedddbf58" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>F1D15</sptc><title id="_5596f525-9364-4c2e-8ef7-b5e3f4a35662">Wall cladding</title><archive-num/><subclause id="_397f4ba1-5f00-47ca-a5e5-5a234d86608b" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_87bfd1b0-74a1-4002-8a8a-0c481bfe5279">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>External wall cladding must comply with one or a combination of the following:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_8ab5585d-0622-435d-abd4-a832d0369494">Masonry, including masonry veneer, unreinforced and reinforced masonry: AS 3700.</li><li id="_00d0f870-4b1c-47f7-b5ab-69dd5a58e07f">Autoclaved aerated concrete: AS 5146.3.</li><li id="_cdf08fb1-90ff-4d26-b025-197be30464f4">Metal wall cladding: AS 1562.1.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_6ab58349-1513-46c7-a1be-1390b996bb4d" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_78460c4a-a105-446f-b8e2-e81cba09dd95">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>The following buildings need not comply with (1):</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_b55df10a-ffe4-4ea3-930c-221f4f739774">A <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1414_4.2.0.xml#_230a3a0f-1539-4b9d-9a2d-8edf732e59dd" id="_55592508-3a75-4d3d-84b8-bb70fd4bc3b3" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">private garage</xref>, tool shed, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1445_0.13.0.xml#_b30a308f-eb9f-4549-a6c1-19d5f32a5272" id="_f8b30227-3221-49d1-b714-51fa1815c0c1" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">sanitary compartment</xref>, or the like, forming part of a building used for other purposes, except where the construction of the garage, tool shed, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1445_0.13.0.xml#_b30a308f-eb9f-4549-a6c1-19d5f32a5272" id="_39a8a125-5be5-4385-ba88-b39c06421280" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">sanitary compartment</xref> or the like contributes to the weatherproofing of another part of the building that is <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_3248cc52-3ee3-446d-950d-14aea0db9991" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> to be weatherproofed.</li><li id="_e411382d-017f-47b4-971c-1917259e584e">An <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1386_0.4.0.xml#_0403e22a-286f-4b36-b369-af068221632b" id="_6f02b55f-a15b-427d-a162-83053790b2df" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">open spectator stand</xref> or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1384_4.0.0.xml#_98f99be0-5c03-48a8-8087-27bc99acc90d" id="_0edbd6e5-a27f-4ac2-8890-ec7b44a4d318" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">open deck carpark</xref>.</li></ol></subclause></clause>